title: Al-Eka Fishworld
description: Al-Eka Fishworld is a sustainable coral and tropical fish farm permaculture business based in Timor Leste.

home.title: Welcome to our coral and ornamental fish permaculture.
home.description: Al-Eka Fishworld Lda is licensed by the Ministry of Agriculture and Fish for aquaculture in Timor Leste for live ornamental fish and coral permaculture for export.  See the sections below for more details on both the corporation and our plans.
